    <section id="Abdera+Project+Incubation+Status">
      <title>Abdera Project Incubation Status</title>
      <p>
        This page tracks the project status, incubator-wise. For more general
        project status, look on the project website.
      </p>
      <p><span class="graduated">The Abdera project graduated on 2008-11-08</span></p>
    </section>
    <section id="Description">
      <title>Description</title>
      <p>
        The Abdera project is an implementation of the Atom Syndication
        Format (RFC4287) and the Atom Publishing Protocol specifications
        published by the IETF Atompub working group.
      </p>
    </section>
